data.description: Welcome Home to your Luxe Oasis!  With over 2,600 expanded under air living space (3,350 sq ft total) your new home features 2 main suites, in which one could serve as your private guest corridor.  Exclusive private upper level suite facing the eastern exposure, chef inspired kitchen and an exclusive office space for those moments when your office need to be just steps away!  You will enjoy the cool Florida fall breeze on your expanded screened lenai.  Thinking of adding a pool or an outdoor kitchen for entertaining your guests?  Your home sits on a 1/4 acre and has plenty of space for both entertainment options.  Your new home awaits your arrival!
